If a sale is conducted as provided in subsection (2) of this section, the proceeds of the sale shall be disbursed in the following order:
Payment for costs associated with the sale;
Payment of amounts due to the person or business providing for the care and feeding of the animal;
Payment to lien holders and creditors pursuant to a court order; and
The remainder, if any, held for the owner for a period of twelve (12) months and, if not claimed at that time, then paid into the district school fund.
